{
  "texts": [
    "Informed consent was obtained for the use of data and samples.",
    "The kidney tissue was dissected from the whole kidney and freshly frozen in Optimal Cutting Temperature embedding media in cryomolds on a liquid nitrogen chilled metal block and stored at -80 o C until ready for experimental use 74.",
    "10-μm-thick sections were cut from the frozen blocks for DART-FISH and flanking sections were used for histopathological assessment by a renal pathologist.",
    "All reagents were listed as in Supplementary Data 1.",
    "A list of genes was selected based on differential expression analysis of snRNA-seq data from human primary motor cortex 46, 48, 50 and a few curated marker genes were added manually to target 121 genes in the human M1C."
  ]
}